                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Richmond</placeName>\n                                        <date>April 7th. 1851</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><addressee>Revd. Isaac. Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dr Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">The books I purchased<lb/> of you when in\n                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>, I have not\n                                        received<lb/> should they not have been sent, you will\n                                        please send<lb/> them by express &amp; oblige yours\n                                        Respectfully</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Lewis Hyman</persName>\n                              </p>"
